---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services">
  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 pt-20 pb-32 sm:pb-40">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <div class="os-window border border-black/[0.04] w-full max-w-lg mx-auto mb-8 sm:mb-12">
        <div class="os-titlebar">
          <span class="os-dot red" />
          <span class="os-dot yellow" />
          <span class="os-dot green" />
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-black/25">Services</span>
        </div>
        <div class="px-8 sm:px-10 py-6">
          <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-black/30 uppercase">Savoir-faire</p>
          <h1 class="mt-2 text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-[#1d1d1f]">Ce que je propose</h1>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-black/40 leading-relaxed">
            Du site vitrine à l'application complexe, chaque projet est unique.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
        <div class="os-window border border-black/[0.04] sm:col-span-2">
          <div class="os-titlebar">
            <span class="os-dot red" />
            <span class="os-dot yellow" />
            <span class="os-dot green" />
            <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-black/25">01 — WordPress</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1d1d1f]">WordPress</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-black/40 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
              Thème sur mesure, WooCommerce, plugins. Je construis chaque site depuis zéro,
              pas de template pré-fait. Design sur mesure, performance optimisée.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-black/5 text-black/50 border border-black/10">Thème sur mesure</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-black/5 text-black/50 border border-black/10">WooCommerce</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-black/5 text-black/50 border border-black/10">Performance</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="os-window border border-black/[0.04]">
          <div class="os-titlebar">
            <span class="os-dot red" />
            <span class="os-dot yellow" />
            <span class="os-dot green" />
            <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-black/25">02 — Sur mesure</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1d1d1f]">Développement sur mesure</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-black/40 leading-relaxed">
              Next.js, Astro, React, Node.js. Des sites ultra-rapides aux applications dynamiques. Stack moderne, déploiement continu.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-black/5 text-black/50 border border-black/10">Next.js / Astro</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-black/5 text-black/50 border border-black/10">React / TypeScript</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-black/5 text-black/50 border border-black/10">Vercel</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="os-window border border-black/[0.04]">
          <div class="os-titlebar">
            <span class="os-dot red" />
            <span class="os-dot yellow" />
            <span class="os-dot green" />
            <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-black/25">03 — Maintenance</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#1d1d1f]">Maintenance & Évolution</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-black/40 leading-relaxed">
              Audit technique, mises à jour de sécurité, amélioration des performances. Je reprends aussi des sites existants.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-black/5 text-black/50 border border-black/10">Audit & Sécurité</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-black/5 text-black/50 border border-black/10">Migration</span>
              <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md bg-black/5 text-black/50 border border-black/10">Performance</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-8 sm:mt-12 os-window border border-amber-200 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-orange-50 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="os-titlebar" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">
          <span class="os-dot red" />
          <span class="os-dot yellow" />
          <span class="os-dot green" />
          <span class="ml-3 text-xs text-black/25">Besoin d'aide ?</span>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 flex items-center justify-between gap-6 flex-wrap">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-[#1d1d1f]">Vous ne savez pas par où commencer ?</h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-black/40">On en parle 30 minutes sans engagement.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/contact" class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-[#1d1d1f] text-white rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black transition-all duration-200">
            Réserver un appel
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
